OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781568171
OL,3,CFifa urged to investigate World Cup
OL,4,Cofficial over 'white power' gesture
OL,6,FFifa is being urged to investigate a
OL,7,FVAR official after he made a 'white
OL,8,Fpower' symbol during a World Cup game
OL,9,Fon Sunday.
OL,11,FShaun Evans, from Australia, was seen
OL,12,Fmaking an upside-down 'okay' symbol
OL,13,Fwith his right hand as the camera cut
OL,14,Fto show the team of video analysts
OL,15,Fahead of Germany vs Curacao, in
OL,16,FHouston, Texas.
OL,26,@wD@Y{q
