OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781568171
OL,3,CFifa urged to investigate World Cup
OL,4,Cofficial over 'white power' gesture
OL,6,FThe gesture - with thumb and
OL,7,Fforefinger touched in a circle and
OL,8,Fother fingers outstretched - was
OL,9,Fdesignated a hate symbol in 2019 by
OL,10,Fthe New York-based Anti-Defamation
OL,11,FLeague.
OL,13,FThe Fare network, a long-time partner
OL,14,Fof Fifa and European football body
OL,15,FUefa in monitoring racist and
OL,16,Fdiscriminatory chants, flags and
OL,17,Fsymbols at international games,
OL,18,Fdescribed the symbol as "neo-Nazi".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
