OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781568171
OL,3,CFifa urged to investigate World Cup
OL,4,Cofficial over 'white power' gesture
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"Advice from our experts is that the
OL,12,Fgesture used clearly resembles an
OL,13,Fupside down 'okay' hand symbol used as
OL,14,Fa 'white power' symbol in global far-
OL,15,Fright circles," it said in a statement.
OL,17,F"Clearly this official should have no
OL,18,Ffurther role to play in this World
OL,19,FCup."
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@OO]yD@AOU
