OL,3,CFifa urged to investigate World Cup
OL,4,Cofficial over 'white power' gesture
OL,6,FEvans' intention with the symbol is
OL,7,Funclear, and Fifa has been contacted
OL,8,Ffor comment.
OL,10,FWhen the sign was designated as a hate
OL,11,Fsymbol, Oren Segal, director of the
OL,12,FADL's Center on Extremism, said
OL,13,Fcontext is key to interpreting whether
OL,14,Fit is hateful or harmless.
OL,16,FHe said at the time there was "enough
OL,17,Fof a volume of use for hateful
OL,18,Fpurposes that we felt it was important
OL,19,Fto add".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
